INVESTMENT PHILOSOPHY


					We seek to provide income, capital appreciation & capital preservation through a disciplined approach of asset allocation, security selection, and portfolio construction which is consistent with long-term wealth building, inflation protection and the realization of your goals				

  ABOUT THE FIRMGarrison Financial Is With You Every Step Of The WayWhat We've Done For Almost Two DecadesGarrison Financial helps individuals and families build wealth and create multi-generational financial legacies. We offer private investors the
sophisticated investment management services normally reserved for large institutions and the very wealthy, and combine them with a
dedication to the highest quality personal service. Sometimes the parts are worth more than the whole.Investment and Portfolio ManagementPersonalized Core Stock, Core Bond, and Balanced AccountsRETIREMENT PLANNING AND MODELINGGuiding You Through Life's Most Important StagesA BOUTIQUE FIRM, A UNIQUELY RESPONSIVE INVESTMENT TEAMRequests And Strategies Are Met And Executed QuicklyMONEY MANAGEMENT SOLUTIONS FOR...Individuals And Institutions Throughout The United States    Our Team...experience is forged on the anvil of knowledge...







